@inth/docs

@inth/docs is the shared docs package for Inth properties. It provides A remark pipeline that flattens MDX components into LLM-friendly markdown. MDX to markdown conversion utilities. llms.txt and topic-scoped llms-full/ .txt generators. Static docs search, content readers, source-grounded answer helpers, and optional bash-tool integration. MDX linting utilities for frontmatter, meta.json , and docs links.

