Package Surfaces

Components The app-owned MDX component contract used by the remark pipeline. Convert convertMdxToMarkdown , writeMdxFileAsMarkdown , and convertAllMdx . Remark individual remark plugins plus defaultRemarkPlugins . LLM generateLlmsTxt and generateLLMFullContextFiles . Search generateDocsSearchFiles , searchDocs , source-grounded answer helpers, and the optional bash adapter. Lint lintDocs and the @inth/docs lint CLI.

