When To Read Which Page

Reach for Components when defining app-owned MDX components for authored docs. Use Convert when you need markdown output from .mdx files. Check Remark for custom plugin order or component flattening behavior. Open LLM when generating llms.txt or topic-scoped full-context bundles. See Search for static indexing, runtime querying, or grounded answer streaming. Use Lint to validate frontmatter, docs URLs, or sidebar metadata.

